    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the dish to a baking tray, cover with <strong>tin foil</strong> and cook in the oven for an initial 20 min or until the pasta is cooked</p><p>Remove the <strong>tin foil </strong>and return the dish to the oven for a further 10 min or until the cheese is melted and golden – this is your <strong>cheesy lentil lasagne</strong></p>",
